{"tid":2212943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK10月推首張常規專輯！回歸預告照讓粉絲們迷惑了：這都是誰？","createTime":"2020-09-22T07:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T09:31:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8798b71a2e0209aed59db6900edec6c884071b08","tid":2212943,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"8月才推出新曲的BLACKPINK，又要攜新曲回歸了，這次帶來的是她們的首張常規專輯。<br />\n<br />\n21日，YG娛樂通過官方SNS公開了BLACKPINK的COMING SOON回歸預告照。 光線陰暗的空間裡，4名成員們背對著鏡頭，只露出了魅惑背影。 雖然看不見正臉，卻依舊感受到強大的氣場。海報上的音源發售日程也吸引了人們的視線。 2020年10月2日美國東部時間0點，韓國時間是同一天下午1點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1efe47797ded0afe5a1b87aa07cd70ac/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-21/130262-875214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1efe47797ded0afe5a1b87aa07cd70ac%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-21%2F130262-875214.jpg&h=dda1d843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回歸照一出立刻掀起了熱議，不為別的，就因為連粉絲們都困惑了，根本分不清誰是誰啊！雖然成員們身高各異，但新照裡她們都只露出了上半身，而且每一位都是身姿曼妙，曲線優美，根本無法從背影中分辨出來。 第一位將頭髮染成雙色，扎成丸子頭。 後三位則都是柔順的披肩長髮，太考驗眼力了。<br />\n<br />\n小編盲猜是ROS&Eacute;、Jennie、Lisa和JISOO，大家怎麼看?<br />\n<br />\n「圖：YG娛樂」"},{"pid":"653d66b9c6bb5c5678e000e8831a67b8e5b7d479","tid":2212943,"uid":313974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"我估：<br />\nJennie <br />\nJisoo<br />\nLisa <br />\nRos&eacute;"},{"pid":"4ac28196bdb36fd376641118654940849db06a14","tid":2212943,"uid":134171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"653d66b9c6bb5c5678e000e8831a67b8e5b7d479","tid":2212943,"uid":313974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"我估：<br />\nJennie <br />\nJisoo<br />\nLisa <br />\nRos&eacute;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"冇個中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d8c7547203917d9651d74c0310cb9223bf5bdb","tid":2212943,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":